xyz_traj_option on
!!sorbate_name ch4_9site* co2_phast* h2_bssp ethanol
!!sorbate_fugacities 1.0 1.0 1.0 1.0

!!carbasis 27.1979 27.1979 30.9998 90 90 120
!!carbasis 150 150 150 90 90 90
carbasis 25.669 25.669 25.669 90 90 90




! MONTE CARLO ONLY ======================================
